reviewText: Mindy Mylrea provides a great workout with the sliders!

excellent work out. My entire body was sore after first time i did it so it is a total body workout. I used an 8 lb medicine ball. I'm not a beginner nor advanced and workout regularly and still found myself sore after this workout. I'm happy I bought it.
this was a great workout, was eazy to implement and worth its weight in gold....doing it over and over  Would give this a four star rating...
